sentences: Matilde Salvador Segarra (23 March 1918 – 5 October 2007) was a Spanish composer and painter.
She was married to the composer Vicente Asencio (1908–1979).
Matilde Salvador died of a stroke on 5 October 2007 in her native Valencia, aged 89.
